<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="favicon-32x32.png" type="image/x-icon" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
    <title>Social Proof</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <img src="bg-pattern-top-desktop.svg" alt="" class="pattern-top" />

    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="text-wrapper">
          <h1>10,000 of our users love our products.</h1>
          <p>
            We only provide great products combined with excellent customer
            service. See what our satisfied customers are saying about our
            services.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rating-wrapper">
          <div class="rating-card">
            <div>
              <img src="icon-star.svg" alt="" />
              <img src="icon-star.svg" alt="" />
              <img src="icon-star.svg" alt="" />
              <img src="icon-star.svg" alt="" />
              <img src="icon-star.svg" alt="" />
            </div>
            <p>Rated 5 stars in Reviews</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rating-card">
            <div>
              <img src="icon-star.svg" alt="" />
              <img src="icon-star.svg" alt="" />
              <img src="icon-star.svg" alt="" />
              <img src="icon-star.svg" alt="" />
              <img src="icon-star.svg" alt="" />
            </div>
            <p>Rated 5 stars in Report Guru</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rating-card">
            <div>
              <img src="icon-star.svg" alt="" />
              <img src="icon-star.svg" alt="" />
              <img src="icon-star.svg" alt="" />
              <img src="icon-star.svg" alt="" />
              <img src="icon-star.svg" alt="" />
            </div>
            <p>Rated 5 stars in BestTech</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="cards-wrapper">
          <div class="card">
            <div>
              <img src="image-colton.jpg" alt="" />
              <div>
                <h2>Colton Smith</h2>
                <span>Verfied Buyer</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p>
              "We needed the same printed design as the one we had ordered a
              week prior. Not only did they find the original order, but we also
              received it in time. Excellent!"
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <div>
              <img src="image-irene.jpg" alt="" />
              <div>
                <h2>Irene Roberts</h2>
                <span>Verfied Buyer</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <p>
              "Customer service is always excellent and very quick turn around.
              Completely delighted with the simplicity of the purchase and the
              speed of delivery."
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <div>
              <img src="image-anne.jpg" alt="" />
              <div>
                <h2>Anne Wallace</h2>
                <span>Verfied Buyer</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p>
              "Put an order with this company and can only praise them for the
              very high standard. Will definitely use them again and recommend
              them to everyone!"
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <img src="bg-pattern-bottom-desktop.svg" class="pattern-bottom" alt="" />
  </body>
</html>
